description: El P + Killer Mike = Run The Jewels. Rap's most dangerous duo have teamed up with Fool's Gold for a free album. Ten tracks of speaker obliterating beats and razor sharp verses, laced with searingly honest emotion and pitch black humor.

For over twenty years, Doug Martsch has been writing and recording music as Built To Spill. The project has a whirlwind of shows heading into 2014, having spent most of the 2013 year on extensive US and European tours. Treefort is excited to welcome BTS back to the festival for three nights. Again this year, members of Built to Spill will curate and perform a festival showcase taking place in the El Korah Shrine, a Treefort 2014 venue. The showcase will span three nights of the festival. Built to Spill will handpick other acts on the showcase lineup and perform a different set each evening.
